Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\1c000000\3cFFFFFF}Gunvarrel製作日記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子太過平凡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天見過愛理之後又有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來的好像挺晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  只是還有點疲勞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這個Gunvarrel是個什麼玩意兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel不就是那個殺人犯監督做出來的動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(545,110)\fs16\1c903318\3cFFFFFF\b1}種子島Robo部\N×\N宇宙糖有限公司\N{\1c2C1AC3}展出Gunvarrel試作2號機！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼把這種東西弄到展會上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇  小亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨乃宮妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小充…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒撞到頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  快給我滾出展會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太不自覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這殺人機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好痛  好痛  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得…  有點傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel居然被討厭到這種地步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明機器人是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是…
