Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-90分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是艾克索斯克爾頓公司展出的概念模型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SUMERAGI通過指控系統——也就是手指來控制6條腿的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
