Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,種子島Robo部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來將啟動我們的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就讓我先來介紹一下這台機器人的製造經過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在距今大約9年前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「實體大型Gunvarrel製造計劃」啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然我也知道在現在以Gunvarrel作為原型並不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(520,210,467,210)\fs12\frz-29\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord1}「實體大型Gunvarrel製造計劃」\N記錄相冊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(370,305,317,305)\fs12\frz-36\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord1}請隨意閱覽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希  你不覺得話說得有點多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀眾都快跑光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.1}但描述一下我們那充滿了愛與勇氣和榮譽的努力過程會比較有衝擊力…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  Gun製造2號機  啟動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橫行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  好醜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那邊那位說「好醜啊」的小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就抱著被騙的心態用IRUO.看一下Gun製造2號機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏有真正的Gunvarrel！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gun製造2號機  一擊破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元氣一發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤  元氣一發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是Gunvarrel就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆史  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  我想再多看一會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽要是知道我給你看了Gunvarrel的話可是會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐  再來一次  再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再表演一次元氣一發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你啦  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤  元氣一發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打…  打家好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…  請朵朵直角！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是阿昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問您現在感想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我們還要更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我會以頭獎為目標的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  這可真是大膽的宣言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.1}瀨乃宮亞希穗同學的姐姐是出演艾克索斯克爾頓公司廣告的美紗希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有告知她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就宣言一下吧  我想她應該已經來到會場內了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  不  你說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  以上便是對種子島Robo部  瀨乃宮亞希穗同學的採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾克索斯克爾頓公司的休息室是在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你最好還是過一陣子再去見美紗姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,84)\frz-12\fs20\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord2}內部人員通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是我啊  亞希穗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們是姐妹  這麼說可能很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們已經七年沒見面了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我還只是個小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是沒認出來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  你看到我製造的機器人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gun製造2號機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是Robo部的大家一起製造出來的機器人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸好久都沒有參與火箭發射的工作了  幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉過身來看看這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說這些話的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨乃宮美紗希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣舉起雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭還沒升空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到沒有  瀨乃宮  給我舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐

